How to run it
Quick backtest (30 days):
bashpython backtest_run.py --days 30
90-day backtest, custom risk:
bashpython backtest_run.py --days 90 --risk 0.015 --min-confidence 0.65 --out results/run1.csv
Grid-search optimizer (finds best parameters):
bashpython backtest_run.py --days 60 --optimize
JSON output (for piping into other tools):
bashpython backtest_run.py --days 30 --json